{"tid":2307781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［月下獨酌］獨守空幃黃翠如行為失常！！！","createTime":"2020-12-01T11:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T17:55:08.000Z","uid":56716,"like":18,"dislike":209,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ab9465b4faff8a69a9641859fcab50f97e99adbc","tid":2307781,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGzB52R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGzB52R.png&h=914d8441&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古有李白「舉杯邀明月，對影成三人」，今有黃翠如「舉手猜情尋，對鏡交朋友」。蕭正楠（Edwin）現正身處隔離營，其妻黃翠如似乎憶夫成狂，做出反常行為！只見翠如對著鏡子七情上面，跟鏡中的自己猜拳，還在照片描述表示有朋友來訪，猜拳勝負未分，下次再續。不少網友好奇Edwin不在身邊，誰替翠如拍照呢？"},{"pid":"72867f4c4023702024a9d940919969715e866406","tid":2307781,"uid":206714,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a0c2541aaa30b723dffb4d0c3f59c74688b875","tid":2307781,"uid":93096,"like":116,"dislike":5,"score":111,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:30:37.000Z","msg":"40歲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488ba6b5c7d818dc559a8525b2618e5313882c27","tid":2307781,"uid":296551,"like":188,"dislike":5,"score":183,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"唔細啦仲做埋啲幼稚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2852a2f1ae804d44e63b06562090162813db56","tid":2307781,"uid":17545,"like":12,"dislike":14,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"吉妹咁好文采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 月下獨酌都識"},{"pid":"5fb763870effb2ea33f14ce9c1d6546935c6d09d","tid":2307781,"uid":48277,"like":143,"dislike":4,"score":139,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T11:33:35.000Z","